Sub-policy 30
https://reklamup.com/privacy.php:
Privacy Policy
Arsus Technologies Ltd (“ReklamUp”, “we”, “us” or “our”) is a Google MCM (Multiple Customer Management) partner ad network that 
provides monetization services to websites and mobile apps.
ReklamUp is committed to being transparent about its data processes and the data collects.
Any data we collect is processed in accordance with regional privacy laws, including GDPR in Europe.
We provide website or app ads via Google Ad Exchange by using Google Ad Manager. See Google Ad Manager and AdX program policies
here
.
Data Collection and Use
If you are a visitor of the apps and websites that we monetize, we may collect certain non-personal, anonymized and 
aggregated information:
- Device model
- Operating system
- Name of website or mobile app
- Country
- City
- Internet connection type
- Internet browser
By collecting these information, we are able to deliver our services and improve them.
We do not collect nor process any personal data.
Data Sharing
We may share information we collect with:
- We may transfer information to our service providers, and other partners who support our business, such as providing 
technical infrastructure services, analyzing how our Services are used, measuring the effectiveness of ads and services, 
providing customer service, or facilitating payments.
- We may share your information to governmental regulatory authorities as required by law.
Manage Your Data
To limit collection of information and interest based advertising, you can opt out
here
.
Children’s Online Privacy Protection
We do not collect any personal data for children under the age of 13 (or 16 in some EU countries).
We may collect non-personal data such as device type or browser.
Security
We take all precautions to keep your information safe. We may keep your information for up to 2 years unless you want it to be deleted.
ReklamUp Website Privacy Policy
- We may collect personal information about you through our Service when you register for an account, such as your name, phone number, email address and payment information.
- We may also collect certain types of technical and usage information automatically, including through cookies and other similar tracking technologies. This information allows us to optimize our website.
- We collect this information with your explicit consent in accordance with GDPR article 6(1)(a) .
- We may use the information we collect through our website to communicate with you, to make payments and provide support.
- We only share your information with your consent or for legal purposes.
Cookies
Our website does not use cookies.
Your Rights
You can request the data we collect about you, request us to delete or update your data by contacting us.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please contact us at support@reklamup.com
